<h1 id="Pattern_skin">  Pattern skin </h1>
Pattern skin provides a CSS based default look and feel - flexible and <span class='externalLink'><a href="http://www.w3.org/">W3C</a></span> compliant. Its layout and color scheme are designed to provide a nice, clean and productive editing environment
<p class='p'>Select a theme to change the look, or tune the entire appearance with CSS or templates.</p>

<div class="foswikiToc" id="foswikiTOC"><span class="foswikiTocTitle">Page contents</span> <ul>
