<p></p>

<h2 id="Browse_available_themes">  Browse available themes </h2>
You may quickly change the appearance of this skin by setting a theme.
<p></p>

<h3 id="Browse_themes">  Browse themes </h3>
Pattern skin has quite some flexibility out of the box. Try one of the provided themes or use them as inspiration for your own theme. <ul>
<li> <a href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkinTheme">Foswiki (default)</a>
</li> <li> <a href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkinTheme2009">Foswiki 2009</a>
</li> <li> <a href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkinThemeFatWilly">Foswiki "Fat Willy" Site Skin</a>
</li> <li> <a href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkinTheme115">Foswiki release 1.1.5</a>
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

