<li> Test <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkin?webheaderart=/pub/System/PatternSkin/header1.gif">header1</a>
</li> <li> Test <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkin?webheaderart=/pub/System/PatternSkin/header2.gif">header2</a>
</li> <li> Test <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkin?webheaderart=/pub/System/PatternSkin/header3.gif">header3</a>
</li> <li> Test <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkin?webheaderart=/pub/System/PatternSkin/header4.gif">header4</a>
</li> <li> Test <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkin?webheaderart=/pub/System/PatternSkin/header5.gif">header5</a>
</li> <li> Test <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkin?webheaderart=">(none)</a> 
</li></ul> 
</li> <li> Set <code>WEBBGCOLOR</code> (currently: <code>#B9DAFF</code>)
</li></ol> 
